%Paper: 9202032
%From: awata@theory.kek.jp
%Date: Mon, 10 Feb 92 21:44:15 JST

%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
%
%                 Screening Currents Ward Identity
%                                and
%      Integral Formulas for the WZNW Correlation Functions
%
%
%
%                          Hidetoshi Awata
%
%
%                         Written by Phyzzx
%
%
%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%  Abstract  %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
%
%      We derive, based on the Wakimoto realization,
%     the integral formulas for the WZNW correlation functions.
%     The role of the ``screening currents Ward identity''
%     is demonstrated with explicit examples.
%     We also give a more simple proof of a previous result.
%
%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
% % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % %
%%%   This is PHYZZX macro package.   % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % %
%% % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % %
%%%  This version of PHYZZX should be used with Version 1.0 of TEX  % %
%% % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % %
%%%   Do not "\input phyzzx" unless you preload or "\input" PLAIN.  % %
%% % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % %
%%%   To preload both PLAIN and PHYZZX, begin your file with	% % % %
%%%  a line "%macropackage=phyzzx" instead of "\input phyzzx".  % % % %
%% % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % %
%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
%%%%%%%  Created by Vadim Kaplunovsky in June 1984.   %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
% % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % % %
%%%%%%%%%%%%  Latest update/debug: September 24, 1984.	  %%%%%%%%%%%%%%
